      • appendClassifications

        protected void appendClassifications​(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​java.util.List<java.lang.String>> assetMap,
                                     java.lang.String typeName)
        Retrieve a mapping of the assets that need to be reclassified. The method will first look up the provided assets to determine only the missing classifications that need to be appended (rather than attempting to blindly append all classifications).
        Parameters:
        assetMap - mapping of assets to consider, keyed by qualifiedName with the value a list of classification names to add the asset to
        typeName - of all the assets
